Invocation Name: home tips
des: Ask Alexa for an interesting tips for home maintenance. When using the skill, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next tip. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill. Sometimes you have something worth fixing at home but do not know how or you didn't even thought that it might cause you issues in future. This tips can help.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
